Connors is working on this new symbiote in his lab to try to help extend Harry's life while they look for a cure, but he winds up turning into the Lizard again somehow and trashes the lab in the process. A few observations based on the HUDs:
Both Spider-men have a L1 and R1 abilities. L1 appear to be different depending on the character. Miles' L1 abilities shows either blue or red coloring (so two different Bio Electricities). R1 appears to be for gadgets (when Miles' uses the gadget in the stealth portion, one of the R1 buttons flashes, and one of the bars above said button goes down by one.) So instead of having one ability or gadget active, it seems we can have multiple ready. 

We see that Miles still has his camoflauge gauge, though Peter does not have. Yet, if you look at Peter's combat: There is a spider icon under his health gauge (this is missing in Miles', which has the camouflage gauge instead.) Perhaps this has to do with Peter either being in the Red Suit or the Black Suit? 

Super Slingshot uses L2 and X. While we see this prompt we see the classic "Point launch" icon in the distance at the same time. This likely means that we can aim (L2 hold) and then press X to slingshot when we find a suitable poles.
